column5: Happy birthday, man!
Happy B-day Cliff!!!
Enjoy your birthday and many more.
Happy happy Cliff. Have a great one and lots more.
Happy B-Day, Cliff!  I'm sure that the fish are mourning this day, but we are all happy for you!  LOL
Happy B-day Cliff now go catch before you need a rod holder for the Gerry Walker. Peace Ken
Happy b-day Cliff, guess you'll be fishing on YOUR day!!
Happy birthday Cliff, I expect to see a fish as long in inches as you are in years tonight.  Nothing like a challenge eh
Happy Birthday Cliff!!!  Go and get another tonight!!!    Did ya get your present yet????

Happy Birthday Cliff and great to have you as  part of the OFC board! You sure have come a long way since you started not that long ago. We all can say that we really enjoy your post and pics. I need to catch more fish like the both of you. Enjoy your day.
LOL  See Monday's fish........38 inches
Happy Birthday Cliff, hope Carole spanks ya
Happy birthday Cliff, looks like you have been catching a few nice presents lately, keep up the good work.
ha ha you are getting older..... Happy birthday bud hope you get all the things you deserve and then some.  Art
Happy birthday fellow fisherman.And wishes of many more.Dan

Thank you everyone for the birthday wishes....and to Alex who started this thread!  Having a great day so far...worked til noon...gonna open some presents soon...have dinner and then hunt some salmon tonight!
The big one is out there waiting for you Cliff!!!!  Happy Birthday!!    Bill
Happy Happy Birthday Cliff !!! Now go catch another chinney......................

HAPPY BIRTHDAY CLIFF!!!!! I hope that you had a great one, from the look of your other post, you got some amazing gifts! You derserve them and I hope you enjoy giving them a great workout!   Angelina's birthday was today too, she turned six. We got her the Baby Alive doll, that she has been asking for, for a year now.LOL   She said it was the best birthday ever, of course.LOL.   Again, Happy Birthday buddy!
Sorry, we're late Cliff..Hope you have a greeaatt day!!!
Happy birthday Cliff. Hope you get the "big one" tonight  :Gonefishing:  :Gonefishing:
No *&%*^&*!!  Happy Birthday!
happy bday!!!!!
happy birthday Cliff. you're probably going to end up with another personal best tonight out there!
Best wishes on your birthday!!!!

Well I wanted to be one of the first ppl to wish you a happy brithday to you . It is my pleasure to have gotten to know you and fish with you Bro in law.  What a week you have been having I hope the rest of it goes as well . CLiff's week in review:
Happy Birthday Cliff, hope you have a great day!  Maureen
Happy, Happy Birthday Cliff....  May the big one be YOURS TODAY..
... and the week isn't over yet!!  Happy birthday Cliff! -Brian
Made another one, eh bud......Here's to you making many many more......TC and tight lines all..........Chuck....
....Best wishes fellow Virgo. Have a great day.
Have a good one Cliff!
Happy b-day Cliff, all the best!
happy birthday Cliff
have a great one
A very Happy Birthday to you Cliff - enjoy YOUR day.
All the Best...  Here's hoping you catch a big 'un...!  I'll try to catch you a carp or maybe some crappie tonight...
happy birthday cliff, have a great day and go land a big one as a present to yourself tonight
Have a great day Cliff. By the way I sure am glad your on team 6.
Happy Birthday Cliff!
Happy Birthday Cliff, have a wonderful day bud  Joey
Happy Birthday and Best Fishes Cliff!
Happy Birthday!!   I couldn't want for a better husband and fishing partner!!  Oh and after today.....I am putting the good hooks back on
Happy Birthday Cliff.......have a good one.  John...
Happy Birthday Cliff!!!!!!!!
Happy Birthday Man keep the reports coming  MTP
Happy Birthday Cliff!  dk
Happy b-day man. Hope you have a good one. Best of luck in future life and future fishing trips!!
Happy Birthday Cliff....see you soon.  Jason
Happy Birthday and many more.  Rick
